						<p>Virtual consultations with Providers are not intended to replace your relationship with your existing primary care physician and are not a substitute for regular use of your primary care physician. Virtual consultations cannot be used for any service that must be provided to you by your regular physician as an in-office follow up to an in-office visit, at no additional charge to you or your health care plan, as required by your health care plan.</p>
